Follow-up: Bilibili has released extremely strict new rules for live broadcasting of Goose and Duck Killing:
The anchor must meet the following requirements: not having been banned since 2022, live broadcasting Goose and Duck Killing for more than 20 days and 60 hours within 2 months, and not having played with strangers during the live broadcast
Only those who meet the above conditions can apply for live broadcasting permission

Yingtan Social Security, a public account under Yingtan, Jiangxi Province, published a post that pensions for retirees in the city have been paid in January. The huge difference between the data of government retirees and ordinary retirees caused public outcry and sparked widespread discussion on the Internet
Some netizens said that the announcement could still be seen on the morning of the 15th, but it has now been deleted.
